    (v_company, 'Shred N Go', 'Travis', '', 'Summer: 5609 St. Louis River Rd Hermantown + 5670 N Cloquet Rd Duluth. Winter: 425 Banks Ave, Superior WI.', 'Net 30', '10:45 am and 11:15 am on Fridays', 'Bi-weekly', '2 box trucks', 'Summer: trucks are parked at the employees'' houses. Winter: indoors at the Superior location — back up to their garage door and run your hose inside. Travis (main contact) will be there; he''s picky and likes to watch, but the nicest dude ever. He loves when we scrub!', 'Basically owner operators, so PICKY', '60 min', '1', '[]'::jsonb, false, 'client'),
